Publish functions:
- Add to module header
- Add extra first parameter func_cb_ptr

Find protoype and update:
- int foo(char)
- int (*)(func_cb_ptr, char)

Order in module header:
- Subscriber then published functions

Error functions:
- Create simple error handler for each subscribed function
- Same proto as supplied version
- Return default value

White list:
- ker_, post_, sys_

Use well defiend hash of prototype for function protype in mod header

Create my own enum to handle the pid and fid
- subscribe
- publish


